{"tid":1102964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【稱30名警員被捕佔全體0.01%　盧偉聰：即99.9%同事努力工作】","createTime":"2019-04-12T05:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T02:31:04.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"d430e9da18f753908afb45059f33310a04db544d","tid":1102964,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"【稱30名警員被捕佔全體0.01%　盧偉聰：即99.9%同事努力工作】<br />\n<br />\n立法會財務委員會今日（4月12日）繼續舉行特別會議，有議員關注涉嫌干犯較嚴重刑事案的警務人員數目，由前年的15人倍增至去年30人。不過警務處處長盧偉聰就指，30名被警務處拘捕的正規警務人員，佔全體警員0.01%，即99.9%同事都努力工作。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰回應時指，對數字感到非常痛心，承認上升幅度大。他指好多世界其他紀律部隊及健全組織都有害群之馬，但強調不會姑息，讓他們去抹殺其他同事的功勞。"},{"pid":"63c581dc45e3fe75a3d803fc0fc1474f48a88952","tid":1102964,"uid":9193,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"同MTR一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebc8ed4128d859fbdd095cefe826b055ffc1bd0","tid":1102964,"uid":1767,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"quote":{"pid":"63c581dc45e3fe75a3d803fc0fc1474f48a88952","tid":1102964,"uid":9193,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"同MTR一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"99.9%準時率"},{"pid":"de47fbc9bb0af21f2ad715fb3eba5594c6024741","tid":1102964,"uid":82532,"like":144,"dislike":2,"score":142,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:51:51.000Z","msg":"係有99.9%未被人捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6066bd01b355a36b0f716218bc0fdb7dfab19f","tid":1102964,"uid":14423,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"無被捕=努力工作？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我公司無人被捕=全部人努力工作？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc3cfaae926598fc3be2c93dc95de2d34952e13","tid":1102964,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit