\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fso20_tc.jsp&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=09fd20e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/so20_tc.jsp</a><br />\n香港人口大約7.48Ｍ，總體罪案54225。比例為0.72%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/facts.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Ffacts.html&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=0b695171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/facts.html</a><br />\n警隊的人數為28 998人，被拘捕的警務人員有38人。比例為0.13%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為維持治安既執法人員，理應道德同守法能力比一般人高得多。<br />\n不過香港警察犯罪率大約係普通人既1/5，而且衰得最多既係偷竊同防礙司法公正，呢兩樣都唔係一時衝動犯案啦。<br />\n<br />\n何況總體罪案係逐單案計，即係當中有一堆人係重犯。<br />\n而警察一俾人捉到就冇得撈。<br />\n淨係計初次犯案既話，警察未必跑輸俾一般人。<br />\n<br />\n咁既數字真係睇到香港警察有幾＂高質＂。"},{"pid":"b098e7f0c350ff4b445cba644113119b49e3163e","tid":1102964,"uid":110389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa858a5e6db517b2a33ba9b15528879eebe38c0a","tid":1102964,"uid":110389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"0.01%，大數學家　<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/09_statistics/csc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F09_statistics%2Fcsc.html&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=0815c1ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/09_statistics/csc.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/so20_tc.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fso20_tc.jsp&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=09fd20e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/so20_tc.jsp</a><br />\n香港人口大約7.48Ｍ，總體罪案54225。比例為0.72